                                                                                               3.13.3e      ENHANCED SECURITY REQUIREMENT
                                                                                                            Employ [Assignment: organization-defined technical and procedural means] to confuse
                                                                                                            and mislead adversaries.

                                                                                                            ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE
                                                                                                            Determine if:

                                                                                                            3.13.3e_ODP[1]     Technical and procedural means to confuse and mislead adversaries
                                                                                                                               are defined.
                                                                                                            3.13.3e[a]         <3.13.3e_ODP[1]: technical and procedural means> are employed to
                                                                                                                               confuse and mislead adversaries.
