                                                                                                                       documentation; procedures addressing the use of honeypots; security plan; system
                                                                                                                       configuration settings and associated documentation; system design documentation;
                                                                                                                       system architecture; list of techniques to be employed to introduce randomness into
                                                                                                                       organizational operations and assets; system audit records; other relevant documents or
                                                                                                                       records].
